I've got it.

10:24.085 --> 10:24.747
This will be soon.

10:24.808 --> 10:26.192
This will be within the next two weeks.

10:26.473 --> 10:28.138
Good fortune to you, sir.

10:28.419 --> 10:28.880
Thank you, sir.

10:28.900 --> 10:29.783
It's been a great pleasure.

10:30.245 --> 10:31.007
Take care.

